WEBVTT

02:12:01.459 --> 02:12:02.834
Even if I forget myself, it’s okay.

02:12:03.626 --> 02:12:05.626
But I’m scared I might forget my mother.

02:12:07.251 --> 02:12:08.834
I don’t know if I’ll forget you too.

02:12:11.376 --> 02:12:15.668
Look, no matter what I say don’t leave me.

02:12:17.293 --> 02:12:18.126
I won’t leave you, child.

02:12:20.043 --> 02:12:21.001
I’ll stay with you.

02:12:22.251 --> 02:12:25.501
I swear, I won’t leave you at all.

02:12:26.126 --> 02:12:27.001
Not at all.

02:12:28.043 --> 02:12:28.834
Shankar!

02:12:30.168 --> 02:12:32.459
I’m scared of what you are becoming.
